1. *Mike* je bio najbolji učenik u razredu. (Mike was the best student in the class.)
2. Devojka je pokazala *Mike*u svoj novi mobilni telefon. (The girl showed Mike her new mobile phone.)
3. *Mike* je bio izuzetno dobar u matematici. (Mike was exceptionally good in mathematics.)
4. Naši prijatelji su nam predstavili njihovog prijatelja *Mika*. (Our friends introduced us to their friend Mike.)
5. Moj brat je veoma dobar sa *Mikom*. (My brother is very good with Mike.)